        "simple-intro-text": "Welcome to Van Dutch Yachts: this Privacy Policy describes the personal data collected through our website, the purposes for which the data is processed and your rights as data subject. \n\nIn order to always be up-to-date on any changes made to this page, we encourage you to consult it regularly.",
