          "settings": {
            "service_type": "DATA CONTROLLER",
            "service_list": "The Data Controller is Cantiere del Pardo S.p.A., with registered office in Via F.lli Lumière 34, Forlì (FC). You can contact the Data Controller by writing to the e-mail address <a style=\"text-decoration:underline\" href=\"mailto:privacy@cantieredelpardo.com\">privacy@cantieredelpardo.com</a>.",
